<li dir="ltr" role="presentation"><a href="https:///diseases/pulmonary-embolism-85?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Heart Failure_factbox_0_mimcking_conditions_3_direct_link_3">Pulmonary Embolism</a>&nbsp;</li>
